Syntax
  open = open (obj)
    Where obj IsA object
      else "You can't open that."

Add to every object
  Is
    Not openable.
    Not open.

  Verb open
    Check obj is openable
      else "You can't open that!"
    And obj is not open
      else "It's already open."
    Does
      Make obj open.
      Say the obj. "is now open."
  End verb.

End add.


